title: 'Ginny & Georgia' Is Not the Next 'Gilmore Girls'
description:
Kate Halliwell and Rodger Sherman talk about 'Ginny & Georgia,' a Netflix show that has been billed as the next 'Gilmore Girls' but most definitely is not.

Hosts: Kate Halliwell and Rodger Sherman
